gaia::base::String gaia::service::WallpaperInfo::getSettingsPage ( ) const

Return the class name of an page that provides a settings UI for the wallpaper.

You can launch this page be starting it with an Demand whose action is MAIN and with an explicit ComponentName composed of getPackageName() and the class name returned here. A empty String will be returned if there is no settings page associated with the wallpaper.
